{"type": "article", "id": 47516, "title": "“华生”出演圣诞爱情广告，腾讯视频在北师大办床单电影院 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-11-23T03:30:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3918, "name": "圣诞"}, {"id": 929, "name": "乐高"}, {"id": 4342, "name": "沃达丰"}, {"id": 261, "name": "百度"}, {"id": 3576, "name": "腾讯视频"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171123110556FidqCahT5fSNYOWw.gif", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24091.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>百度发布品牌广告《努力更懂你一点》</b></a>，机器人小度在里面频繁出镜，百度最爱挂在嘴边的产品和技术也悉数出现。“今天百度更懂你”也是 2017 年百度大会的主题。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=e0505xlno0j&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24100.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为了征集“不负青春好时光”全国校园故事，腾讯视频在北师大珠海校区做了个“床单电影院”的快闪营销</b></a>。收集了 200 多条高校学生的床单，剪裁制作成为露天荧幕，在校园里播放电影。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711231037163hxz6G0A21TiNvgk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561224\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123103810tG8PqQbnuIRJkFUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564967\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123103821eWPt2pG6NrzMKLqi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565044\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b>“<a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24103.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">华生”马丁·弗里曼出演沃达丰圣诞广告</a></b>，用六个篇章讲述了一则“动人”的爱情故事。由奥美伦敦操刀，今年 1 月，他们赢得了全球最大的移动电话运营商之一的沃达丰在英国的广告业务。<a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24103.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里观看视频</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123104429JWkidNnb0pIO9q26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.368571\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123104440I62ZvcQFypnS0ROm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.367143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123104450pEalnPeTwI9Zv12d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.364286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/22/an-oriental-hero-saves-the-xmas-day-in-australia/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>乐高澳大利亚的圣诞广告里出现了东方元素。</b></a>在这支名为《Save Santa》的定格动画中，来自东方、武术高超的神秘老人解救了流落在床底的圣诞老人，最后两个人合力完成了一辆乐高小车，幸福快乐地去送礼物了。广告拍的挺萌，创意代理商是&nbsp;CHE Proximity。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=s0508zwfygo&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/22/supor-releases-a-series-of-colorful-gif-posters-and-a-tvc-toshow-what-is-real-nutritious/\" rel=\"nofollow\">为推销破壁料理机新品，苏泊尔（SUPOR）发布了一组色彩亮丽的海报</a></b><strong>，</strong>代理公司是利欧数字旗下 Match·马马也。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711231056039Pa2k8tVlHZpi7Bd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.938095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711231055225rYXFM40j1mixqWp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.975000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>最后，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/fake-ad-operation-used-to-steal-from-publishers-is-uncovered-1511290981\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>一家丹麦的广告技术公司 Adform 表示他们发现了一个大型、复杂的广告欺诈计划 Hyphbot</b></a>，自至少 8 月份以来就一直在执行，Hyphbot 创建了超过 34000 个不同的域名和超过一百万个不同的网址，用来欺骗广告商让他们认为自己的广告投放在了《经济学人》、《金融时报》、《华尔街日报》和 CNN 上。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：腾讯视频</p>"}